casebody.data:
E.T., Petitioner-Petitioner,
v.
DIVISION OF MEDICAL ASSISTANCE AND HEALTH SERVICES, Respondent-Respondent,
and
Hudson County Board of Social Services, Respondent. C-688 September Term 2017
080480 Supreme Court of New Jersey. March 9, 2018

To the Appellate Division, Superior Court:

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-000403-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied, with costs.
